<br>Now what to fix without throwing off the whole balance.  I would suggest minor changes that really doesn't change offensive or defensive ability.  A example would be to put offensive and defensive disciplines on different timers.  This would allow a warrior to actually use mighty strike for example once a hour, without fear of needing defensive 5 minutes later. Other ideas could be simple clicky-button type skills that have 15 minute re-use timers on em.  Such as a automatic crippling blow once every 15 minutes or whatever.  These ideas would not change the overall damage output by a small margin, but increase the enjoyability of the class.<br><br>Just my opinion.  <br><br>Sprite Brokenheart<br>Warlord <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uvaraho1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Varaho1</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 532<br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/13/02 9:52:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1895.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_ac.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Re:</span><hr size=1> Taunt is a joke no really it is like some sick and twisted cruel joke of a skill, the other classes just cant comprehend how much this skill sucks. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uslagfestbloodsoul.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Slagfest Bloodsoul</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/13/02 10:55:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteel